
BEM : Block Element Modifier 

-- VD -- 
Laptop : Block 
Keyboard, mouse , touchpad , screen : Element 

* Modifier áp dụng cho block 
Laptop big , laptop smaill : Modifier for block 
smaill Keyboard , smaill screen : Modifier for Element

Block__Element--modifier 
Block--modifier 
Block__Element 

laptop 
laptop__keyboard, laptop__touchpad,Laptop_screen 
laptop--smaill, laptop--expensive ,laptop--big
laptop__touchpad--smooth,laptop__screen--scale 

<-- EX1 -->
Block : flash-message 
Element:image,title,description(desc),button.
Modifier: primary , secondary. 
----
<-- Block 1 vs 2 -->
flash-message 
flash-message_image. flash-message_title, flash-message_descripion,flash-message_button

Block 1 : flash-message_title--primary,flash-message__button--primary
Block 2 : flash-message_title-secondary,flash-message__button--primary






Từ vựng : 
Tiêu đề : title 
danh mục : category



 
